The nutritional food market is experiencing significant growth due to the increasing health consciousness among consumers, rising cases of chronic diseases, and the growing awareness about the benefits of a balanced diet. The market is driven by factors such as the rising geriatric population, busy lifestyles leading to a demand for convenient and healthy food options, and the focus on preventive healthcare. Technological advancements in food processing and packaging have also contributed to the expansion of the nutritional food market. Additionally, the COVID-19 pandemic has further bolstered the demand for products that boost immunity and overall health.

